All stock...
1500 engine.
Coil over plug distributorless ignition.
Fuel injection.
Stock exhaust w/catalytic converter.
Automatic, continuously variable transmission.

Manufacturer ratings:
70 hp (-at-) 4500 rpm, 82 lb-ft (-at-) 4200 rpm.
44 hp (-at-) 3320 rpm (+/- 2280 rpm), 258 lb-ft (-at-) 400 rpm.

45.5 mpg lifetime average over 33,000+ miles.

